      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and represents a rare find for any serious buyer. It has been meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a flawless exterior with no scratches, dents, or imperfections. The interior is equally pristine, featuring leather that looks and smells brand new, with every electronic component functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound with a full service history, offering a driving experience that feels exactly like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. This is an exceptional example of the model, perfect for a collector or someone who demands the absolute best.",
