    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a project or a budget-friendly way to get on the road? This car has character and is ready for someone with a little know-how to bring it back to its full glory! While it definitely needs some mechanical attention and cosmetic TLC, it offers a great foundation for a mechanic's special or a dedicated restorer at a price that can't be beat.",
